2016-12-26T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一d都唔正 即刻開始病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntake care<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n病完啦 都三個禮拜前既事喇<br />\n依家漸漸覺得佢唔再吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4877c77b208fbef46e4ab0887d354b32fbf9d2a9","tid":55274,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間當然重要 <br />\n但係每日匿係屋企喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好累<br />\n自己又做唔到啲咩 唔想郁 咩都唔想做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下,又話「每日匿係屋企喊」<br />\n原來每日既意思係岩岩先第二日咋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃子華:想當年呢....呢~咪上年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:半年,已經無日日喊鬼喊忽無咁頹,不過都係未放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7874eedafe0f58ad83853b25729204605e801e3","tid":55274,"uid":21797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間當然重要 <br />\n但係每日匿係屋企喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好累<br />\n自己又做唔到啲咩 唔想郁 咩都唔想做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下,又話「每日匿係屋企喊」<br />\n原來每日既意思係岩岩先第二日咋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃子華:想當年呢....呢~咪上年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:半年,已經無日日喊鬼喊忽無咁頹,不過都係未放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未分手之前都有啲事發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ee9b3eff7cca96e90fee21c8521f266c81df05","tid":55274,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T19:32:04.000Z","msg":"搵野學下 約下FD/自己出下街 <br />\n有新對象就好快冇事架啦<br />\n加油<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgBjV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgBjV.gif&h=7b63adb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a646f0a1388e549d4aa9ce5e82097b9776ce8b00","tid":55274,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T20:49:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間當然重要 <br />\n但係每日匿係屋企喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好累<br />\n自己又做唔到啲咩 唔想郁 咩都唔想做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n下,又話「每日匿係屋企喊」<br />\n原來每日既意思係岩岩先第二日咋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黃子華:想當年呢....呢~咪上年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:半年,已經無日日喊鬼喊忽無咁頹,不過都係未放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未分手之前都有啲事發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nsorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如呢?"},{"pid":"7a5e8a6ff16c01fb3974693e3647518db9877dfa","tid":55274,"uid":9288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:14:28.000Z","msg":"前兩日分...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d90a1abb0d86853851a4c23116bd40629d7edbe","tid":55274,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:19:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友幫唔少<br />\n一定要傾訴多啲<br />\n傾越多 越快好返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年我淨係識屈埋<br />\n晚晚走落海傍鳩行聽歌<br />\n正常咁讀書同搵工<br />\n年幾先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2084ab380b97b7cee512475d078397b98ad54dfa","tid":55274,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工作 音樂？<br />\n識多啲異性</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b671a6fe7410c289439377d818e9b8421be9678","tid":55274,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:22:52.000Z","msg":"頹足一個月了，愈來愈嚴重，但其實無分過手，因為都無開始過，仲係朋友，出街時仲要扮無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03181d2c93416d5f13daebda722edeb3a174173a","tid":55274,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>朋友幫唔少<br />\n一定要傾訴多啲<br />\n傾越多 越快好返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年我淨係識屈埋<br />\n晚晚走落海傍鳩行聽歌<br />\n正常咁讀書同搵工<br />\n年幾先好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n初戀之後分手已經唔點痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e69000ad4fad6810cb545d87951a3fe871e6575","tid":55274,"uid":50931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T21:31:59.000Z","msg":"想當年周日至四叫雞，五六飲酒，過左四星期，即刻冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bfdba16e35b7a6bec5a5223377c1575132061b","tid":55274,"uid":41436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T22:30:08.000Z","msg":"冇搵過任何人，完全靠自己，都用左一年多啲先可以放低，不過間唔中都會掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最緊要識得臨崖勒馬叫自己stop.時間同忙係主要因素，有時讀書忙到真係可以一兩日冇諗起過佢，夜晚好攰可以立即訓著冇得情緒氾濫亂諗嘢，不妨搵啲嘢充實自己，時間真係可以令你慢慢走出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6f9f4c915907139e30b656ec42bbe478f2eb37","tid":55274,"uid":68661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T22:59:23.000Z","msg":"日日起身之後飲酒食煙 飲到攰就訓 訓醒不停loop 餓就求其少少野再訓過<br />\n訓唔到就睇劇 唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將fb ig wtspp全部停曬 唔想見到佢同佢現任既野 個心好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9c93740db059363bb3a7a400015235039a0fa5","tid":55274,"uid":18745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:26:23.000Z","msg":"我都係散左幾日<br />\n日日都喊 明明同自己講唔好停係度了 <br />\n但仲係好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經狠下心刪晒fb d 相 希望快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家希望盡快食到野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每日都唔識肚餓咁 唉<br />\n放完假會plan 去做運動 實行短期目標<br />\n<br />\n樓主 共勉之"},{"pid":"2b1e03bc4f46bf569ee876f1892d1345ed37d6e5","tid":55274,"uid":48823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"我會諗好多新計劃畀自己 <br />\n例如係運動 旅行 音樂 閱讀 義工 <br />\n只要有興趣就得<br />\n感覺好似變成一個新嘅自己<br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣散咗後開始行山 開始返教會 去咗轉旅行 將生活填得滿滿 好快冇嘢<br />\n<br />\n但最重要係要塵封舊愛所有嘢 見都廢事 一見就瀨嘢<br />\n<br />\n利申: 散咗兩年"},{"pid":"7d73e3d2e10d73b35771f5389e7e4f0060c01166","tid":55274,"uid":38603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"學我將放唔低既野寫低<br />\n最好就寫到幾多就幾多<br />\n其間你會喊到仆街<br />\n但係一日一日咁過<br />\n到最後你會發現其實呢段感情無咩大不了<br />\n只係自己一直將段感情神化左<br />\n頹唔係唔得 但係係唔係一定要咁樣落去？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/54011/page/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/54011/page/2?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"977626d97cd6f208c14b7724d8c0102e1c8e4617","tid":55274,"uid":38603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:05:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/54011/page/2?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/54011/page/2?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"1369699a45863fec87cb84581bc15fc35e95d8c7","tid":55274,"uid":57314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"我都係平安夜 不過係上年 有頂綠色既聖誕帽 到依家都放唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c69c2391a557b0951b1b221d593b214a69e2ffa","tid":55274,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"佢俾帽我帶完，仲想利用我激條仔！<br />\n<br />\n係呢刻我完全死心，唔當佢係人，<br />\n<br />\n咁就走出左"},{"pid":"c8f455f644676130acadac3dbc6f2190ab6abe56","tid":55274,"uid":69339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以麻醉下自己<br />\n我唔想諗起佢，真係好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac91e01ced95f6fe3e82aef55cb87569eed72cf","tid":55274,"uid":11171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:41:59.000Z","msg":"分左岩岩好一年 未脫離到<br />\n但真係會愈諗愈攰<br />\n冇左好傷心果種感覺<br />\n個人都變得靜左唔想理咁多野 好攰"},{"pid":"b0beb2cc5c35e73088a51b09d1ab062c462a08b1","tid":55274,"uid":40652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"搵個第二個"},{"pid":"0f3cb22b31e689f332f35ecfc0cf85fed59f9559","tid":55274,"uid":63244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"瘋狂睇心靈雞湯同聽d單身更幸福既歌"},{"pid":"6ec8c7e47de2cd40cf42a320621f2fefb9e1f860","tid":55274,"uid":25478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"出街鳩行 撩叔叔嬸嬸公公婆婆傾計<br />\n佢地會同你講人生講歷史<br />\n愈聽得多 原來自己段戀愛一啲都唔轟烈<br />\n慢慢冇再諗邊個岩邊個錯 生活正常返<br />\n但有佢既消息 仍然會想知"},{"pid":"d3cb28082bc45d17b541d7453b4961ed525c6da0","tid":55274,"uid":62183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T04:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初頭會成日搵朋友傾、出街<br />\n但佢地始終唔會無時無刻陪到同安慰自己<br />\n我當時日日loop Running Man、Mr Bean等等呢類搞笑野<br />\n雖然唔識笑，甚至會喊，但感覺上啲笑聲好似陪住自己咁<br />\n同埋我唔會迫自己唔好諗住對方<br />\n想諗佢既時候就諗，慢慢就會覺得攰而唔再諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nloop咗幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nloop左3星期到，有時未更新新一集，就每日不斷翻睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a9f80d7fb1d654fe24ea0a7df52a08947153fe","tid":55274,"uid":19266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間當然重要 <br />\n但係每日匿係屋企喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好累<br />\n自己又做唔到啲咩 唔想郁 咩都唔想做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇得pm你絲打，我有你的經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293ce7e41668376f8a2afe7215d6209e078bb555","tid":55274,"uid":9856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩都分左 唉 以後開始新感情真係要好好了解清楚先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個啱"},{"pid":"6da72dca6be5b1c1d11e4ebf54e3e708b59a3922","tid":55274,"uid":9856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:02:55.000Z","msg":"兩個月了 我未走到 扮醒 扮從來冇一齊過 對方冇野 只得我懷念多麼諷刺"},{"pid":"d4b308f1fa22c89e51d7ad9916187b3b88804e16","tid":55274,"uid":43470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"今日分手 初戀拍左2年<br />\n我仲係好愛佢 我唔想有咩改變<br />\n但係繼續既話只係傷到自己。。<br />\n<br />\n依家成個腦都係同佢既回憶 我唔知自己應該點做"},{"pid":"3695d17a2b7dddf2c413ab63f06e78b986afa022","tid":55274,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c9983dd7f31e88e0afbe952c211ed7d8b99a9f2","tid":55274,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:20:51.000Z","msg":"每當無聊時就會睇佢ig會唔會有新嘢<br />\n早排見到有條仔follow咁佢，佢今日就follow返條仔。<br />\n啱啱又見到有條仔follow咗佢<br />\n個心好痛，好唔想再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cf52a9ab32cea177bdc99173ed2ea6e110cc1a","tid":55274,"uid":28201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每當無聊時就會睇佢ig會唔會有新嘢<br />\n早排見到有條仔follow咁佢，佢今日就follow返條仔。<br />\n啱啱又見到有條仔follow咗佢<br />\n個心好痛，好唔想再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知我唔係佢邊個，無權再管佢嘅一切<br />\n但我好唔想佢識到新男仔 開展新一段戀情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3368b263aaa6ec9c1fa8ff218c7341c3c876481","tid":55274,"uid":21797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T14:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時